OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's push for more powers for
OL,7,Fthe Welsh Government has begun with
OL,8,Fopening moves at both ends of the M4.
OL,10,FAfter the new First Minister told the
OL,11,FPrime Minister he wanted to start
OL,12,Fnegotiating on further devolution, in
OL,13,FWestminster the party's group of MPs
OL,14,Fhas launched a parliamentary bid for
OL,15,Fthe transfer of more power.
OL,17,FMeanwhile the UK Government has said
OL,18,Fit will look at proposals from the
OL,19,Fprevious Labour Welsh Government to
OL,20,Fdevolve power and funding of youth
OL,21,Fjustice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
