OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779207074
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,FThat account was described as broadly
OL,7,Faccurate by others familiar with the
OL,8,Fconversation who added that it didn't
OL,9,Fmention that the First Minister
OL,10,Fbrought up the matter of independence.
OL,11,FThey expressed surprise that this was
OL,12,Fmentioned in the first conversation
OL,13,Fwith the Prime Minister.
OL,15,FThat can be seen as the opening of a
OL,16,Fpolitical divide, with opponents
OL,17,Faccusing Plaid Cymru of playing down
OL,18,Fthe issue of independence during the
OL,19,Felection campaign.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779207074
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,FHowever, Rhun ap Iorwerth repeatedly
OL,7,Fsaid that, while a strong supporter of
OL,8,Findependence, it was not an issue for
OL,9,Fthis election, ruling out a referendum
OL,10,Fwithin the next four years.
OL,12,FToday's move in the UK Parliament sees
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru making another push for
OL,14,Fthe transfer of further powers by
OL,15,Fusing an amendment to the King's
OL,16,FSpeech. It's unlikely to be passed
OL,17,Fbecause Plaid Cymru can only count on
OL,18,Fthe support of its four MPs and a
OL,19,Fsmall number of others.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779207074
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,FThe amendment calls for a new Wales
OL,7,FBill - the parliamentary mechanism by
OL,8,Fwhich powers have been transferred in
OL,9,Fthe past.
OL,11,FIt calls for the devolution of rail
OL,12,Finfrastructure, the Crown Estate,
OL,13,Fjustice and policing, water and social
OL,14,Fsecurity. It also calls for the
OL,15,Ftransfer of powers over a wide range
OL,16,Fof other areas, including power to set
OL,17,Fincome tax bands here in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
