OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779207074
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,FThe former Welsh Conservative leader
OL,7,FAndrew RT Davies criticises the First
OL,8,FMinister for "pursuing" independence,
OL,9,Fadding that "Broken promises like this
OL,10,Fare the reason public trust in
OL,11,Fpoliticians is at an all time low."
OL,13,FThe focus on possible future transfer
OL,14,Fof powers comes on a day when the UK
OL,15,FGovernment has announced it's looking
OL,16,Fat the devolution of aspects of the
OL,17,Fjustice system.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@WO]qD@MOUsD@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
