SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779207074
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,FIt's published a White Paper - a
OL,7,Fdocument which sets out proposed law
OL,8,Fchanges - into the future of youth
OL,9,Fjustice, including the possibility of
OL,10,Ftransferring some funding and power to
OL,11,Fthe Welsh Government.
OL,13,FA Labour source said that, "This White
OL,14,FPaper includes the devolution of youth
OL,15,Fjustice funding to the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment and a greater role for the
OL,17,FWelsh Government in the youth justice
OL,18,Fsystem.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779207074
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru ramp up the push for more
OL,4,Cpowers for Wales
OL,6,F"This is the culmination of work by
OL,7,Fthe Wales Office and Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice with the previous Welsh Labour
OL,9,FGovernment to strengthen the
OL,10,Fdevolution settlement, ensuring a
OL,11,Ftangible benefit to people's lives.
OL,13,F"While Plaid remains silent on whose
OL,14,Ftaxes will be hiked or which services
OL,15,Fwill be cut to fund their independence
OL,16,Fagenda, Labour is delivering on our
OL,17,Fmanifesto commitment and getting on
OL,18,Fwith the job."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
